item.title: CVE-2024-2495|2024-03-15T13:07:05.436Z -- FriendlyElec -- FriendlyWrt
item.description: Cryptographic key vulnerability encoded in the FriendlyWrt firmware affecting version 2022-11-16.51b3d35. This vulnerability could allow an attacker to compromise the confidentiality and integrity of encrypted data.
